  "description": "Diagnose and prevent UNABLE_TO_LOCK_ROW + parent-record contention in record-triggered, scheduled, and screen flows by mapping the implicit lock chain and applying decouple patterns (Platform Events, Queueable handoff, Scheduled Paths). NOT for general flow bulkification \u2014 see flow-bulkification. NOT for fault-path catch logic \u2014 see flow-rollback-patterns.",
  "file_location": "skills/flow/flow-record-locking-and-contention",
  "id": "flow/flow-record-locking-and-contention",
  "inputs": [
    "Flow XML or design + expected concurrent transaction volume",
    "Object hierarchy (parent / child / Master-Detail relationships)",
    "Per-day transaction profile (peak qps on the parent object)"
  ],
